utils = require "Utilities"
local min = Component.GetProperty("minValue") local max = Component.GetProperty("maxValue") local width = Component.Call("Height") - Component.Call("handle.Height") local scale = 1 local prev_value = min - 1
function Reset() min = Component.GetProperty("minValue") max = Component.GetProperty("maxValue") if max - min > 0 then scale = width / (max - min) else scale = 0 end
Component.Call("handle.LuaCall", "Reset") end
function InitState() Update() end
function ValueSet( value )
Component.SetProperty( "Value", utils.RoundToInt( value ) ) Update() end
function ValueGet()
return utils.RoundToInt(Component.GetProperty("Value"))
end
function Update()
local value = utils.RoundToInt(Component.GetProperty("Value"))
if (value < min) then value = min else if (value > max) then value = max end end Component.SetProperty("Value", value)
handleX, handleY = Component.Call("handle.Position") ourX, ourY = Component.Call("Position")
handleY = utils.RoundToInt(scale * value)
Component.Call("handle.MoveTo", handleX, ourY + handleY)
if prev_value ~= value then prev_value = value notify = Component.GetProperty("Notify") if notify ~= nil then Component.CallByAddress(notify, "LuaCall", "Notify", Address, value) end end
--[[ local value = Component.GetProperty("Value") if (value < min) then value = min else if (value > max) then value = max end end Component.SetProperty("Value", value)
handleX, handleY = Component.Call("handle.Position") ourX, ourY = Component.Call("Position")
handleY = scale * value
Component.Call("handle.MoveTo", handleX, ourY + handleY)
out.shane( "Updating VSlider: Prev value "..prev_value..", New value "..value )
if prev_value ~= value then prev_value = value notify = Component.GetProperty("Notify") if notify ~= nil then
out.shane( "Notifying" ) Component.CallByAddress(notify, "LuaCall", "Notify")
end end --]]
end
function Layout(children) Update() end

local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent()) local textfield = UIComponent(this:Find("text_field"))
function OnSelect() local txt = textfield:LuaCall("Value") parent:LuaCall("SearchForGame", txt) end
